question: PTID
conformity: String with max length of 10 characters
notes: Follow your Center’s Patient ID scheme; must be the same as the UDS visit.

question: ADRC name
notes: Use your Center ID. Valid codes are available here: https://naccdata.org/center-ids

question: ADRC Visit Number
notes: This must be the same as the UDS packet visit number

question: Packet Code
response_labels: IDS, Initial Visit Packet, DS Module

question: Form Date
notes: This must be the same as the UDS packet visit date (i.e., Form A1 form date)
